A node web application that authnticates the user against an LDAP server such as ActiveDirectory and redirects to Kndling.

Uses a shared secret authentication as defined in https://support.kindlingapp.com/kb/article/11/

Uses express library, deployable on CloudFoundry


INSTALLATION

1. Make sure you have node installed.
2. Install dependencies
	npm install

3. Run the app
	npm app.js

